name: Pudgy Penguins
description:
Pudgy Penguins is a collection of 8,888 NFTs, waddling through Web3. Embodying empathy & compassion, Pudgy Penguins are a beacon of positivity in the NFT Space. Each holder receives exclusive access to experiences, events, and more. 

Join the Huddle now and spread good vibes across the meta. 

[pudgypenguins.com](https://pudgypenguins.com)

name: ArcadeNFT
description:
By combining interactive games with amazing artforms from both new talented artists, renowned creators & famous brands.

We aspire our series of collectables to be fun, unique & addictive to play! Join us on an adventure where we take the classical arcade games into the future of NFTs.
